There are several good indicators on the drivers station that will show the state on interaction between the drivers station and the robot.

Something else to watch is the lights in the driver station software. Does the robot code light turn red when you go into teleop (even if briefly)? If so, something is causing the code to crash. A frequent culprit is modifying one object from two different places at the same time.
